snippet.title: DUST FLEET - First Look & Gameplay (New 4X RTS Space Sim)
snippet.description:
In this Video we are Check Out the 4X RTS Space Sim "DUST FLEET" in 2K.
Share your thoughts and leave a comment

Assume command of a battle fleet and deploy immediately to the Dust Zone, commander. Our main food supply station has gone dark and the United Earth Nations (UEN) needs to know why in this 4X RTS space sim. Manage your ships, control space stations, and watch your back.

TITLE: Dust Fleet
GENRE: Indie, Strategy
DEVELOPER: Orbiting Disco
PUBLISHER: Freedom Games
RELEASE DATE: 2023

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/406160/Dust_Fleet/
